detect Sasame's medicine this time?

30
00:02:17,054 --> 00:02:20,349
Isn't it strange that
Master Jiraiya's that sharp?

31
00:02:20,432 --> 00:02:22,017
Hey, hey...

32
00:02:22,393 --> 00:02:26,355
Remember when Sasame talked
about Hanzaki and said he's a traitor?

33
00:02:26,772 --> 00:02:28,023
That's how I knew...

34
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:32,736
Hanzaki told me everything...

35
00:02:34,572 --> 00:02:39,201
When Orochimaru came to this land,
there were those among us

36
00:02:39,285 --> 00:02:43,414
who wanted to use his strength
to revive the clan

37
00:02:43,497 --> 00:02:48,669
and those that saw his evil intent
and said we should not join him.

38
00:02:49,587 --> 00:02:53,883
Hmm... so that's why you guys
were chased out of your village.

39
00:02:54,425 --> 00:02:59,430
Yes. It was probably Orochimaru's idea

40
00:02:59,513 --> 00:03:01,974
we were chased out of our village

41
00:03:02,057 --> 00:03:05,853
as traitors who were getting
in the way of a revival of the clan.

42
00:03:07,897 --> 00:03:11,108
When Sasame called Hanzaki a traitor,

43
00:03:12,067 --> 00:03:16,363
I knew that Sasame had ties to a group
that was on Orochimaru's side.

44
00:03:24,580 --> 00:03:25,748
Fool!

45
00:03:25,831 --> 00:03:26,874
Hey, Pervy Sage!

46
00:03:27,416 --> 00:03:29,418
Just wait a minute!

47
00:03:29,501 --> 00:03:31,045
I'm prepared!

48
00:03:32,838 --> 00:03:38,093
Sasame, you did it so that
you could meet Arashi... Isn't that so?

49
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:45,267
I'm sorry...
that was the only thing I could do.

50
00:03:45,976 --> 00:03:47,269
Master Jiraiya!

51
00:03:47,353 --> 00:03:50,856
Sasame did it only because
she wanted to see her cousin.

52
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:52,775
Please forgive her!

53
00:03:52,858 --> 00:03:55,319
I'm asking you to forgive her too!

54
00:03:55,402 --> 00:03:58,489
The law of the Shinobi
is a strict thing...

55
