I can't just acquit her like this.

56
00:04:08,248 --> 00:04:11,335
Then punish me first!

57
00:04:13,045 --> 00:04:19,009
I promised I'd help Sasame
see her cousin Arashi!

58
00:04:19,093 --> 00:04:23,222
If I don't fulfill that I'll have twisted
my Way of Ninja!

59
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:25,641
Master Jiraiya, me too!

60
00:04:25,724 --> 00:04:29,770
Now now, wait a minute!
It's not as if I'm gonna eat her alive.

61
00:04:30,145 --> 00:04:31,522
– Huh?!
– Oh?

62
00:04:31,897 --> 00:04:35,901
Sasame, Hanzaki was worried that

63
00:04:35,985 --> 00:04:39,196
you might leave your village to
look for Arashi...

64
00:04:52,042 --> 00:04:55,546
After you escort us to
Orochimaru's hideout,

65
00:04:55,629 --> 00:04:57,965
