like that anyway!

74
00:05:23,824 --> 00:05:25,868
I feel cheated that
I gave you more credit!

75
00:05:25,951 --> 00:05:29,538
He, hey...
It's all right once in a while, right?

76
00:05:29,621 --> 00:05:32,708
There's something called
socializing for adults...

77
00:05:47,514 --> 00:05:48,640
There it is...

78
00:05:49,141 --> 00:05:51,226
Leave the rest to us.

79
00:05:51,727 --> 00:05:54,563
Sasame, be careful going back
to the inn.

80
00:05:55,230 --> 00:06:00,652
Don't worry! I will absolutely
bring Arashi back!

81
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:06,825
Please take care of Arashi!

82
00:06:07,284 --> 00:06:08,786
Leave it to me!

83
00:06:08,869 --> 00:06:12,039
