00:07:01,547 --> 00:07:02,881
Hey!

96
00:07:02,965 --> 00:07:06,093
Th-The frog spoke!

97
00:07:06,176 --> 00:07:10,597
Hey, it's been a while!
Sakura, this is Gamakichi.

98
00:07:11,849 --> 00:07:13,392
Gamakichi?!

99
00:07:13,642 --> 00:07:16,311
