to be anything fishy...

103
00:07:37,499 --> 00:07:39,918
There doesn't seem to be
a trap at the entrance.

104
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:47,676
Arashi...

105
00:07:57,352 --> 00:08:00,522
There's nothing to it around here.

106
00:08:14,745 --> 00:08:15,746
Hmm...

107
00:08:16,330 --> 00:08:17,414
What shall we do?

108
00:08:17,789 --> 00:08:20,751
It seems there's no choice
but to split up into three.

109
00:08:20,834 --> 00:08:23,962
My instinct tells me
it's the middle one!

110
00:08:24,046 --> 00:08:26,506
Wait!
What the heck?!

111
00:08:27,466 --> 00:08:30,052
At times like this, it's especially
important to move carefully...

112
00:08:40,312 --> 00:08:42,898
All right, I'll go this way!

113
00:08:44,066 --> 00:08:45,150
That's it?!

114
00:08:45,234 --> 00:08:48,528
So what's so different from
my instinct and that, Pervy Sage?

115
00:08:48,737 --> 00:08:51,240
Well, it's a question of feeling...

116
00:08:51,990 --> 00:08:55,827
If you haven't found anything
after 30 minutes, come back.

117
00:08:56,119 --> 00:08:58,121
Got it?
Yeah...

118
00:08:58,747 --> 00:09:03,418
Naruto, Sakura, the two of you
should proceed together.

119
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:08,590
Listen, from this point forward,
it's the first avenue of hell.

120
00:09:08,924 --> 00:09:11,009
A demon might appear,
or a snake might appear.

121
00:09:11,093 --> 00:09:12,594
Take them on mindfully!

122
00:09:13,095 --> 00:09:14,096
Yup!

123
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:17,766
I understand!

124
00:09:19,601 --> 00:09:22,062
