131
00:10:15,407 --> 00:10:17,951
Because guests would be
arriving from far away,

132
00:10:18,035 --> 00:10:22,831
I was directed by Lord Orochimaru
to entertain.

133
00:10:23,832 --> 00:10:26,752
I'm guessing
it's a type of fox raccoon ghost...

134
00:10:27,627 --> 00:10:30,797
If you're saying
I'm some raccoon or fox,

135
00:10:30,881 --> 00:10:36,261
you ought to come over here
and check to see if I have a tail or not.

136
00:10:36,762 --> 00:10:40,974
Oh, this path was right on...

137
00:10:41,933 --> 00:10:44,061
How about yours, Naruto?

138
00:10:46,646 --> 00:10:49,358
Sakura, be careful!

139
00:10:49,775 --> 00:10:52,486
There's no telling what sort
of traps there might be...

140
00:10:52,569 --> 00:10:54,112
Yeah...

141
00:10:54,571 --> 00:10:56,573
– Oh?!
– Naruto?!

142
00:10:58,075 --> 00:11:00,202
And you were the one who
said to be careful!

143
00:11:00,285 --> 00:11:02,537
It was an ingenious trap floor!

144
00:11:07,334 --> 00:11:10,670
Oh!
What the hell is next!

145
00:11:13,090 --> 00:11:14,383
Sakura!

146
00:11:17,469 --> 00:11:19,096
Naruto!

147
00:11:25,185 --> 00:11:26,728
It's my fault...

148
00:11:27,979 --> 00:11:29,147
Naruto!

149
00:11:29,231 --> 00:11:31,274
What the hell...

150
00:11:35,445 --> 00:11:37,239
I can't get out...

151
00:11:37,948 --> 00:11:39,157
What're you doing?!

152
00:11:39,241 --> 00:11:41,952
You screamed in such
a misleading way, I totally thought...

153
00:11:42,619 --> 00:11:44,746
Give me a hand!

154
00:11:45,288 --> 00:11:46,915
You're really a handful!

155
00:11:49,334 --> 00:11:50,460
Ya saved me...

156
00:11:50,544 --> 00:11:52,838
Really! I'll go first!

157
00:12:05,058 --> 00:12:06,601
Naruto...

158
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:10,689
It's all right now.

159
00:12:11,064 --> 00:12:12,065
Here!

160
00:12:15,777 --> 00:12:16,862
Huh?!

161
00:12:28,832 --> 00:12:30,125
Naruto!

162
00:12:35,589 --> 00:12:36,715
Naruto!

163
00:12:38,341 --> 00:12:40,177
Naruto!

164
00:12:40,802 --> 00:12:43,263
Sakura...

165
00:12:43,889 --> 00:12:46,349
Naruto?! Are you all right?

166
00:12:48,226 --> 00:12:50,270
Don't worry about me.

167
00:12:50,353 --> 00:12:53,023
You need to hurry and
get out of this trap hallway!

168
00:12:53,523 --> 00:12:54,524
But...

169
00:12:54,608 --> 00:12:58,904
I said go! I'll follow behind for sure!

170
00:12:59,863 --> 00:13:00,864
Really?

171
00:13:00,947 --> 00:13:04,284
Yeah... I'll catch up in no time!

172
00:13:09,956 --> 00:13:11,333
You'd better come, no matter what.

173
00:13:12,042 --> 00:13:13,460
It's a promise, you know...

174
00:13:20,967 --> 00:13:24,179
The sake doesn't seem
tampered with.

175
00:13:24,804 --> 00:13:27,641
So what kind of plot has been prepared...?

176
00:13:31,978 --> 00:13:34,397
Just as I'd expect from
the Village Hidden in Sound...

177
00:13:34,481 --> 00:13:37,984
Are you planning to put a Jutsu
on me using music?

178
00:13:39,027 --> 00:13:43,240
The music isn't only for guests.
It's for myself...

179
00:13:44,449 --> 00:13:45,784
I see...

180
00:13:46,368 --> 00:13:49,079
What do you play for your heart?

181
00:13:52,874 --> 00:13:56,169
Music for my own funeral...

182
00:14:05,053 --> 00:14:08,557
Trying to seduce me...
You've underestimated this Jiraiya!

183
00:14:33,623 --> 00:14:38,962
Escorting the guest to
the underworld is my last mission.

184
00:14:41,464 --> 00:14:42,882
A suspended ceiling?!

185
00:14:47,679 --> 00:14:50,682
