and get out of this place!

186
00:14:51,391 --> 00:14:52,809
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

187
00:14:55,687 --> 00:14:57,147
This is torture!

188
00:14:57,731 --> 00:14:59,065
What the hell?!

189
00:14:59,524 --> 00:15:01,192
Give me a hand!

190
00:15:01,276 --> 00:15:04,321
We need to build up our Chakra
and create the Rasengan!

191
00:15:04,404 --> 00:15:06,281
Don't be absurd!

192
00:15:06,364 --> 00:15:09,117
We can't stretch
our bodies beyond this!

193
00:15:09,784 --> 00:15:11,870
My muscles are cramping up!

194
00:15:11,953 --> 00:15:14,873
Man! I've gotta do something...

195
00:15:15,373 --> 00:15:16,833
– What!
– Huh?!

196
00:15:17,375 --> 00:15:18,418
What?!

197
00:15:18,501 --> 00:15:20,003
– Water?!
– Water!

198
00:15:33,308 --> 00:15:34,976
Looks like I've been saved.

199
00:15:36,478 --> 00:15:38,647
Hey, get outta my way!

200
00:15:38,730 --> 00:15:41,399
Oh, it's you, Naruto.

201
00:15:41,483 --> 00:15:44,736
Gamakichi, is there
a way out somewhere?

202
00:15:44,819 --> 00:15:49,658
Don't know!
I was flushed down here too.

203
00:15:52,118 --> 00:15:54,412
So it's no good...

204
00:15:54,496 --> 00:15:56,665
Hey, are you all right?

205
00:15:56,748 --> 00:15:58,667
How could I be all right!

206
00:16:21,648 --> 00:16:23,817
Naruto's taking a long time.

207
00:16:24,484 --> 00:16:25,860
Maybe I should go back...

208
00:17:07,318 --> 00:17:10,822
It's admirable that
you made it this far, Sakura.

209
00:17:11,573 --> 00:17:14,033
Is that Kabuto's voice?!

210
00:17:14,743 --> 00:17:16,494
Isn't it ironic?

211
00:17:17,203 --> 00:17:21,040
During the Chunin Exam
in the Village Hidden in the Leaves,

212
00:17:21,124 --> 00:17:24,043
you were the only one
that dragged the team down,

213
00:17:24,127 --> 00:17:26,171
but yet you're the one
to make it this far.

214
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:28,089
I'm not by myself!

215
00:17:28,715 --> 00:17:31,176
Naruto and Master Jiraiya
will be here right away!

216
00:17:32,010 --> 00:17:35,638
Where's Sasuke?
He is all right, isn't he?

217
00:17:36,347 --> 00:17:40,477
Shouldn't you be worried about
Naruto and Master Jiraiya,

218
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,604
and not Sasuke?

219
00:17:45,899 --> 00:17:51,070
Well, it may very well be that those two
are no longer in this world anymore.

220
00:17:51,529 --> 00:17:52,530
No way...

221
00:17:55,116 --> 00:17:59,078
There's no way Master Jiraiya and Naruto
would be taken down that easily!

222
00:17:59,162 --> 00:18:01,080
I wonder if that's so?

223
00:18:01,873 --> 00:18:06,169
Maybe you dragged Naruto
down like you always do?

224
00:18:08,755 --> 00:18:09,839
So I'm right ...

225
00:18:11,299 --> 00:18:12,425
Naruto...

226
00:18:18,223 --> 00:18:21,142
If you're worried
you should go and see...

227
00:18:22,977 --> 00:18:25,814
