of me attacking

228
00:18:25,897 --> 00:18:28,358
and you can't come out
from behind the pillar.

229
00:18:28,650 --> 00:18:33,321
If someone like you were
on my team,

230
00:18:33,404 --> 00:18:36,324
I don't know how many lives
I would need.

231
00:18:36,407 --> 00:18:37,408
I can too...

232
00:18:37,742 --> 00:18:39,118
I can too!

233
00:18:48,878 --> 00:18:50,213
Substitution Jutsu?!

234
00:18:52,632 --> 00:18:54,384
Substitution again?!

235
00:18:58,471 --> 00:19:00,932
I can too...
When I fight, I fight!

236
00:19:02,016 --> 00:19:04,352
As I thought, this is all you've got...

237
00:19:06,312 --> 00:19:08,857
It's about time I put an end to this.

238
00:19:09,607 --> 00:19:13,903
I can't keep Lord Orochimaru waiting
for no reason any longer, you see.

239
00:19:14,904 --> 00:19:15,947
Orochimaru?!

240
00:19:24,914 --> 00:19:27,458
Now...shall we see...

241
00:19:29,711 --> 00:19:32,130
just who will be stealing
scrolls from whom?

242
00:19:35,133 --> 00:19:36,426
We'll fight to the death!

243
00:20:04,913 --> 00:20:09,250
No! I'm different from how I was...then!

244
00:20:11,461 --> 00:20:12,712
I wonder if that's true...

245
00:20:26,225 --> 00:20:27,518
It can't be...

246
00:20:30,188 --> 00:20:32,690
Even if you put up a bluff,
I can foresee ...

247
00:20:34,025 --> 00:20:37,362
You are already...finished.

248
00:21:10,770 --> 00:21:15,525
When I recalled the parts one by one,

249
00:21:15,608 --> 00:21:21,864
I felt as though
I had understood everything

250
00:21:21,948 --> 00:21:26,536
Faded words

251
00:21:26,619 --> 00:21:32,709
which I kept so close to me

252
00:21:32,792 --> 00:21:38,256
Speechless nights,

253
00:21:38,339 --> 00:21:42,260
a hint of warmth,

254
00:21:43,886 --> 00:21:49,308
and this distant yearning for you

255
00:21:49,392 --> 00:21:52,186
I live,

256
00:21:52,270 --> 00:21:58,401
simply repeating this cycle

257
00:22:00,403 --> 00:22:04,323
Held in my two hands

258
00:22:04,407 --> 00:22:09,996
A droplet of time

259
00:22:11,289 --> 00:22:17,879
Softly clutching forgotten memories

260
00:22:17,962 --> 00:22:20,715
Lost words

261
00:22:29,390 --> 00:22:33,227
I'll keep these thoughts...

262
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:40,234
I'm scared.
What is this intimidating feeling?

263
00:22:40,777 --> 00:22:43,696
My legs are weak and
I don't have any strength in my body.

264
00:22:44,322 --> 00:22:47,408
I thought I'm not the same person
as I was in the past.

265
00:22:47,909 --> 00:22:50,036
I must stop. Calm down.

266
00:22:50,119 --> 00:22:53,039
These guys are here,
which means Sasuke is definitely here!

267
00:22:53,706 --> 00:22:57,418
I need to fight!
I came here to save Sasuke!

268
00:22:58,461 --> 00:23:01,380
Next time, "Two Heartbeats:
Kabuto's Trap"

